                     java.lang.String currencyTo,

        This is the parametrized constructor of the class.
        Parameters:
        date - The date when transaction was made. Date format: YYYY-MM-DD.
        rate - The exchange rate between the specified currencies.
        currencyFrom - The currency ISO to be converted (ex. USD, EUR, etc).
        currencyTo - The currency ISO to convert into (ex. USD, EUR, etc).
        insertTime - The exact date and time when the transaction was made.
